The '''Khra shuttle''' was a type of [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] used by [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]] bodyguards. A fast unit capable of carrying at least two Noghri, one was used by [[Sakhisakh]] and [[Barkhimkh]] in their mission to [[Pakrik Minor]].

